    educational: "Portability allows a surviving spouse to use any unused estate tax exclusion from their deceased spouse. This can significantly reduce or eliminate estate taxes when the surviving spouse eventually passes away. The DSUE is calculated on the deceased spouse's estate tax return and becomes available for the surviving spouse's estate.",
