    question: "Original issue discount (OID) on a bond must be:",
    options: ["Included in the holder's gross income annually using the constant yield method — even though no cash is received; the OID accrues over the life of the bond, increasing the holder's basis","Recognized only when the bond is sold or matures","Excluded from income if held to maturity","Treated as a capital gain only"],
    correctAnswer: 0,
