    examTip: "Remember the age requirement (70½) and the direct transfer rule for QCDs; a check written to the charity by the IRA owner does NOT qualify.",
    memoryAid: "QCD: *Q*ualified *C*haritable *D*istribution = *Q*uite *C*lever *D*onation (for those over 70½)",
