    options: ["Recognized gain of $100,000 (limited to boot received); basis of new property is $500,000","No recognized gain; basis of new property is $500,000","Recognized gain of $300,000; basis of new property is $700,000","Recognized gain of $100,000; basis of new property is $600,000"],
