    question: "ABC Corporation, a calendar-year C corporation, had the following information for the current year:\n\n*   Qualified research expenses (QREs): $500,000\n*   Base amount for research credit: $400,000\n*   Work Opportunity Credit (WOTC) wages: $100,000\n*   General business credit carryforward from prior year: $10,000\n*   Tax liability before credits: $70,000\n*   Tentative minimum tax: $15,000\n\nWhat is the amount of general business credit ABC Corporation can use in the current year on Form 1120?",
    options: ["$52,500","$60,000","$67,500","$70,000"],
