    examTip: "Pay close attention to the age of the individuals when calculating HSA contributions, as those 55 and older are eligible for additional catch-up contributions. Remember to verify if the question concerns a single HSA account or separate accounts.",
    memoryAid: "HSA: Health Savings Account. Remember the triple tax advantage: deductible contributions, tax-free growth, and tax-free withdrawals for qualified medical expenses.",
