    question: "ABC Partnership incurred $200,000 of qualified research expenses (QREs) in 2023. The partnership agreement states that all income and losses are allocated equally among the three partners: Alice, Bob, and Carol. However, the agreement also specifies that research credit will be allocated based on each partner’s capital contribution. Alice contributed 50% of the capital, Bob contributed 30%, and Carol contributed 20%. What amount of research credit, based on the QREs, should be reported on Alice's Schedule K-1?",
