    examTip: "Pay close attention to the specific terms of the partnership agreement regarding allocations. The default allocation for income/loss may not apply to all items.",
    memoryAid: "Remember to check the partnership agreement (or operating agreement for an LLC taxed as a partnership) for allocation rules specific to items like research credit, depreciation, or guaranteed payments.",
